105
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,020
Liang Huaiji,

106
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:42,940
Your Highness bestowed me my name.

107
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,860
I was young and ignorant,

108
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,220
