120
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,060
If he knows

121
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:15,660
it’s written by

122
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:18,460
Liang Huaiji with calm character
and high sensitivity

123
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,700
who His Majesty praised before,

124
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:21,740
