125
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:24,700
When he praised you,

126
00:06:26,220 --> 00:06:28,340
I totally forgot what happened before.

127
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:34,340
Madam Zhang,

128
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:35,580
Her Highness is meeting someone.

129
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,660
What thing can be more

130
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,580
