151
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:30,060
= Du Yan, courtesy name Shichang =
Besides, more than 30 years ago,

152
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:30,980
after the Treaty of Alliance of Song
and Liao was signed,

153
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:32,460
