Indeed, they are.

159
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:45,420
= Wang Su, courtesy name Zhongyi =
The war in Shaanxi just ceased.

160
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:47,340
Yuanhao retreated,

161
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,820
but we also lost a dozen of

162
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,420
