173
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:19,220
checked Chuyue,

174
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:20,780
I asked him every detail.

175
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,460
Physician Hu said,

176
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:24,020
Chuyue is still

177
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,620
