196
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:34,540
Like now,

197
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,220
Chuyue is having a fever.

198
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:37,540
You shouldn’t bring her out

199
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,660
