215
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:26,740
It’s not relevant to anyone.

216
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:30,380
It’s not relevant to anyone?

217
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:38,460
= Zhao Chuyue, 8:00 am of 30th =

218
00:10:45,700 --> 00:10:46,620
This doll

219
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:49,500
