233
00:11:27,220 --> 00:11:29,620
Chuyue’s sickness is not relevant to it.

234
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:32,460
But I just heard

235
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:34,460
two days ago,

236
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:37,220
Huirou was mumbling to the moon

237
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:38,420
by the lake in the backyard,

238
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:40,700
and this is found

239
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:41,900
