243
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,740
= Territory of Song and Foreign Countries =

244
00:11:54,740 --> 00:11:57,820
It is impossible to cede our territory.

245
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:00,820
But to cope with this,

246
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:03,580
we can learn from Han and Tang.

247
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,780
Learn for Han and Tang?

248
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:10,940
Marriage.

249
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:15,220
The currently leader of Liao

250
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,980
