258
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:41,620
Chuyue has been cursed by Huirou,

259
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,340
but you don’t want to give the order
to investigate it.

260
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,060
Why?

261
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:52,500
Alright.

262
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:55,700
I’m not hoping you to give any care to it.

263
00:12:57,460 --> 00:12:58,260
I just want you

264
00:12:58,260 --> 00:12:59,860
