of Happiness and Tranquility.

266
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,460
I’m going to see His Majesty.

267
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,220
His Majesty is unwell,

268
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:08,980
