274
00:13:27,220 --> 00:13:29,460
Aren’t you worried that
His Majesty would blame you after he knows?

275
00:13:35,940 --> 00:13:37,620
I will look into this thing.

276
00:13:42,860 --> 00:13:43,900
The evidence is here.

277
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:45,740
The witness is Maid Xu.

278
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:47,380
