279
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:49,540
Your Highness always value rules.

280
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:52,060
If you don’t take swift actions against

281
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:54,020
that evil girl,

282
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:55,940
