283
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,500
Your Highness,

284
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:05,180
I have something

285
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:07,420
that might be relevant to
what Madam Zhang is talking about

286
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,860
to tell now.

287
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:12,460
How’s that possible?

288
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:15,980
Bring Huirou here.

289
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:23,940
Madam Zhang,

290
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:26,220
for the girl Huirou you are talking about,

291
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:28,540
is she about 5 or 6 years old,

292
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:30,460
this tall?

293
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:34,900
Yes.

294
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:38,620
She just turned 5,

295
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:39,740
and is that tall.

296
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:42,420
Madam Zhang,

297
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:45,100
Maid Xu saw Huirou

298
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:46,260
praying in the backyard

299
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:49,180
at about 21:15, am I right?

300
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:55,740
Yes.

301
00:14:58,540 --> 00:14:59,420
The other night,

302
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:01,900
when I left the Hall of Peace

303
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:03,460
after I sent the medical book transcripts,

304
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:05,060
I accidentally went into the backyard

305
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:06,460
because I doesn’t know the way.

306
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:08,220
I saw

307
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,940
a barefooted girl in white dress

308
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:11,220
praying to the moon.

309
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:13,660
When I was trying to find the way,

310
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:15,580
I heard the sound of night watches of 21

311
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,860
before I met her.

312
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,940
So I must’ve met her at about 21:15.

313
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:22,620
Did you hear

314
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:25,780
what she’s praying?

315
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:26,820
She said

316
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:28,180
her father was sick,

317
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:29,780
she was willing to

318
00:15:30,180 --> 00:15:31,380
suffer ten times more than her father

319
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:32,940
for the well-being of her father.

320
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:41,380
Why would you go to the lakeside?

321
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:42,540
Mother,

322
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,460
you are having my sister or my brother

323
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:45,980
in your belly,

324
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:48,460
you shouldn’t worry about other things.

325
00:15:49,380 --> 00:15:51,460
Now Madam Zhang is telling Her Highness

326
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,620
you are cursing Chuyue.

327
00:15:53,980 --> 00:15:55,540
How can I not worry?

328
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:58,020
Chuyue is my sister,

329
00:15:58,380 --> 00:15:59,140
I love her.

330
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:00,620
How would I curse her?

331
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:02,940
Did she ever use witchcraft

332
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:05,460
to curse others?

333
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:07,300
Absolutely not.

334
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:09,740
I saw her at the South Gate that day.

335
00:16:10,460 --> 00:16:11,660
I saw this girl

336
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:13,020
running to the lake with barefoot

337
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:14,500
and tears on her face.

338
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,340
I thought she’s a maid

339
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:17,420
who’s been wronged

340
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:18,820
and wanted to kill herself.

341
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,940
So I followed her to the lakeside.

342
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:23,460
But then I heard her

343
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:25,180
praying to the moon for her father.

344
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:27,460
Later, she was found by others,

345
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:29,140
so she left immediately.

346
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,940
She didn’t curse others,

347
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:33,220
nor bring this thing.

348
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:36,740
Nonsense!

349
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,940
A maid praying for her father?

350
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:42,860
What a great show!

351
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:47,660
Who are you?

352
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:50,220
Why did you make this up

353
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:51,140
to protect the murderer?

354
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,220
If you did meet a

355
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:54,780
maid you don’t know at the lakeside,

356
00:16:55,460 --> 00:16:56,580
why can you still remember

357
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:58,940
what she said

358
00:16:58,940 --> 00:16:59,740
and did

359
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:00,620
after few days?

360
00:17:02,100 --> 00:17:03,180
That day, I

361
00:17:03,180 --> 00:17:04,540
followed her

362
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:06,660
because she’s young

363
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:07,980
and it was dark,

364
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:08,980
which made me worried.

365
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:11,940
Besides, her praying for her father

366
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,500
with tears

367
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:14,980
and sincerity

368
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:17,900
impressed me deeply.

369
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:19,740
That’s why I remember it so clearly.

370
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:24,980
Okay.

371
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:29,260
Suppose you did meet such a person.

372
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,180
Many concubines in the palace

373
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:34,260
and stewardesses

374
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:36,380
adopt daughters.

375
00:17:36,740 --> 00:17:38,580
It can be any girls.

376
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,420
Are you so sure

377
00:17:40,980 --> 00:17:42,460
that the girl is Huirou?

378
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:45,460
I am not entirely sure

379
00:17:45,860 --> 00:17:47,340
that the girl I met the other day

380
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:50,100
is the Huirou Madam Zhang is talking about.

381
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:51,940
But I

382
00:17:52,340 --> 00:17:54,380
have a distinct impression on

383
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:55,500
the girl who prayed for her father.

384
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:57,100
In case it is wrong,

385
00:17:57,820 --> 00:17:59,860
can you give me a moment,

386
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:01,420
some pen and paper

387
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:03,780
to paint the girl

388
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:05,580
and the scene I saw

389
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:06,820
the other day?

390
00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:13,180
You say you didn’t curse her,

391
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:15,380
then why did you go there?

392
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:16,220
For what?

393
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:18,140
= Princess Huirou =

394
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,180
Tell me!

395
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,620
If you don’t feel guilty,

396
00:18:21,620 --> 00:18:22,980
why can’t you say it?

397
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:26,020
Tell me!

398
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:33,700
Tell me!

399
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:39,420
Don’t be angry, mother.

400
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:41,420
I didn’t do anything bad.

401
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:45,220
I swear if I lied,

402
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:49,340
the love from father, Her Highness and mother

403
00:18:49,340 --> 00:18:51,020
will be taken away from me forever.

404
00:18:58,860 --> 00:19:00,420
Madam Zhang is very overbearing.

405
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:04,900
If you don’t tell the truth and show the evidence,

406
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,700
she won’t let you go.

407
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,740
I must see Her Highness

408
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:13,220
and explain it to her.

409
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:15,340
I can’t let her wrong you.

410
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:40,100
She is the princess.

411
00:20:07,620 --> 00:20:09,100
Who lets you

412
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:11,620
give false evidence

413
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,260
and lie to the imperial family?

414
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,660
I didn’t know

415
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:18,100
eunuchs in the palace

416
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,460
are so good nowadays

417
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:22,020
that can just draw

418
00:20:22,140 --> 00:20:23,180
such a painting easily.

419
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:26,460
Who would believe

420
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:28,020
that he’s not trained and taught by someone.

421
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:35,980
Tell me,

422
00:20:37,180 --> 00:20:38,620
who made you do this?

423
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:40,740
Huirou,

424
00:20:42,420 --> 00:20:43,260
Concubine Miao,

425
00:20:45,580 --> 00:20:46,740
or someone else?

426
00:20:53,540 --> 00:20:54,940
I dare not lie.

427
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:56,460
What I said is the mere fact.

428
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:02,740
What about now?

429
00:21:03,460 --> 00:21:04,580
Still the mere fact?

430
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:08,140
Do you really think you can do everything you want

431
00:21:08,140 --> 00:21:09,460
with someone’s protection?

432
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:11,980
Don’t you fear that I’ll tell His Majesty

433
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:13,300
and sentence you for deceiving him?

434
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:13,980
Enough.

435
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:18,180
It is very disgraceful

436
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:19,300
to slap a eunuch.

437
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:28,860
He’s Liang Huaiji,

438
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:31,500
who is working in the Imperial Academy.

439
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:33,980
He doesn’t even know

440
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:34,980
Huirou is Princess Fukang.

441
00:21:35,780 --> 00:21:37,260
How can he be instigated to do this?

442
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:42,540
Princess?

443
00:21:46,140 --> 00:21:47,100
I don’t know

444
00:21:47,620 --> 00:21:48,660
she’s a princess.

445
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:51,660
I called the princess’s name directly.

446
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:52,860
Please punish me.

447
00:21:58,540 --> 00:22:01,020
What a great show!

448
00:22:04,020 --> 00:22:05,420
Ignorance can be forgiven.

449
00:22:21,460 --> 00:22:23,100
Ask Princess Fukang to come here.

450
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:26,860
No need to let Madam Miao know.

451
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:28,940
If she asks,

452
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:31,420
tell her I want to

453
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:32,540
test what Huirou learned these days.

454
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:34,140
Yes, Your Highness.

455
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:45,500
Among all the daughters of the imperial families,

456
00:22:46,660 --> 00:22:49,140
the daughter of Duke Jian is the best candidate.

457
00:22:50,140 --> 00:22:52,220
I’ll draft the proposal now.

458
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:55,300
His Majesty woke up for two hours

459
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:56,580
after lunch yesterday,

460
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:58,020
and fell asleep again.

461
00:22:58,260 --> 00:23:00,500
It’s 9 a.m. now and he still hasn’t woken up.

462
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:02,340
Physicians said

463
00:23:02,340 --> 00:23:04,060
he’s out of danger,

464
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:04,820
but

465
00:23:06,180 --> 00:23:08,100
The proposals from Xia Song, Han Qi

466
00:23:09,100 --> 00:23:11,180
and Fan Zhongyan asking for punishment…

467
00:23:11,780 --> 00:23:12,700
Keep them here for now.

468
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:14,300
Especially the one from Fan Zhongyan.

469
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:17,940
Xiwen was impeached for communicating
with the enemy

470
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:21,780
and giving demoralizing speech just before the war,

471
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:24,940
but his management over military
and civil affairs in Yan’an

472
00:23:25,220 --> 00:23:26,260
is flawless.

473
00:23:26,460 --> 00:23:28,580
He went there for just a year,

474
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:30,620
but he solved the water depletion in dry season

475
00:23:30,860 --> 00:23:33,500
by digging a dozen of wells

476
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,340
and opened schools.

477
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:38,300
He won his reputation.

478
00:23:38,980 --> 00:23:40,260
I think this time His Majesty

479
00:23:40,260 --> 00:23:41,940
is sadder than angry.

480
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:43,220
Some people

481
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:46,580
will be demoted,

482
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:51,220
but will also be reused again.

483
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:53,740
Madam Miao has arrived.

484
00:23:58,620 --> 00:24:00,660
Why do you come here?

485
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:01,500
Your Highness.

486
00:24:02,100 --> 00:24:03,700
I told Ms. Xiu to ask Huirou to come here.

487
00:24:06,420 --> 00:24:07,260
Stand up.

488
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:14,620
Your Highness, I heard what’s going on here.

489
00:24:15,460 --> 00:24:16,740
Huirou is so young.

490
00:24:16,900 --> 00:24:18,420
How would she know witchcraft?

491
00:24:18,820 --> 00:24:20,460
Besides, she loves her sister so much.

492
00:24:20,740 --> 00:24:22,380
She would never do that.

493
00:24:22,900 --> 00:24:23,900
Please find the truth

494
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,140
and justify Huirou.

495
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:28,580
You believe Huirou,

496
00:24:28,860 --> 00:24:29,980
then what are you worrying about?

497
00:24:30,940 --> 00:24:32,740
Do you think I’ll be biased?

498
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:36,900
Sit down.

499
00:24:48,860 --> 00:24:50,300
I lost my mind.

500
00:24:51,100 --> 00:24:53,740
I rushed here

501
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:56,140
when I heard Lady Zhang wronged Huirou.

502
00:24:57,940 --> 00:24:58,940
Wrong?

503
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,700
Did I?

504
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:03,540
Besides,

505
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:07,340
who else in this world

506
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:09,300
is more afraid that

507
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:10,860
Chuyue will share His Majesty’s love.

508
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:12,380
She is young,

509
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:15,660
so I think she’s not capable

510
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:17,100
of doing this alone.

511
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,740
If no one told her to do this,

512
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:22,860
someone must’ve helped.

513
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:27,980
Just now I’ve sent someone

514
00:25:27,980 --> 00:25:29,020
to bring Huirou here.

515
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:33,180
She must’ve missed you on the way.

516
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:36,820
But now since you are here,

517
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:38,180
just stay a bit longer.

518
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:41,620
Let’s find out

519
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:43,660
the truth

520
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:45,060
in front of all of you.

521
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:47,700
Both Huirou and Chuyue

522
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:49,420
are the apples in His Majesty’s eyes,

523
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:51,020
and my children.

524
00:25:52,060 --> 00:25:53,460
I won’t let anyone of them

525
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:55,700
be wronged.

526
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:58,700
= Gao Taotao =
Do you think

527
00:25:58,860 --> 00:26:00,220
Huirou will be jealous

528
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:01,500
for His Majesty

529
00:26:01,500 --> 00:26:02,420
loves her sister?

530
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:05,100
Huirou is bright and outgoing.

531
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:06,980
And she’s young.

532
00:26:07,060 --> 00:26:07,860
She’s surrounded by

533
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:08,700
dignified people

534
00:26:08,700 --> 00:26:09,780
= Zhao Zongshi =
like Her Highness and Madam Miao.

535
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:12,300
Her maids are upright and honest too.

536
00:26:12,620 --> 00:26:14,220
How can she know witchcraft?

537
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,340
I’m not saying

538
00:26:16,340 --> 00:26:17,540
she did this.

539
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:20,420
I was thinking

540
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,540
if Huirou

541
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:23,900
is a bit jealous of Chuyue.

542
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:26,420
After all,

543
00:26:27,860 --> 00:26:30,180
Chuyue’s mother is Lady Zhang,

544
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:32,540
who takes His Majesty’s attention away
from Concubine Miao.

545
00:26:32,940 --> 00:26:34,060
Concubine Miao must

546
00:26:34,060 --> 00:26:35,180
hate Lady Zhang.

547
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:38,900
Then it is understandable for Huirou

548
00:26:39,140 --> 00:26:40,100
to be jealous of Chuyue.

549
00:26:40,980 --> 00:26:42,140
Madam Miao is gentle and magnanimous.

550
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:43,380
She won’t hate others.

551
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:02,260
Huirou,

552
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,460
greet Lady Zhang.

553
00:27:06,580 --> 00:27:07,580
Yes.

554
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:15,140
I do not deserve your salute.

555
00:27:17,580 --> 00:27:18,380
Today

556
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:20,380
I just hope Princess Fukang

557
00:27:20,380 --> 00:27:21,780
can tell us what happened in the backyard,

558
00:27:21,900 --> 00:27:23,140
and clear the curse on Chuyue.

559
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,180
If it can cure my baby,

560
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:28,620
she doesn’t need to give salute to me,

561
00:27:29,900 --> 00:27:31,140
I can even

562
00:27:31,140 --> 00:27:32,060
salute to her.

563
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:37,700
Huirou,

564
00:27:39,820 --> 00:27:41,060
did you go to the backyard

565
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,500
the other day before yesterday at night?

566
00:27:43,900 --> 00:27:44,980
Yes.

567
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:48,420
What for?

568
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:57,580
Is father getting better?

569
00:27:59,620 --> 00:28:00,620
He is much better.

570
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:03,660
He does not need acupuncture treatment anymore.

571
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:06,780
That’s great.

572
00:28:08,700 --> 00:28:11,020
You prayed to the moon in the backyard.

573
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:12,460
The heaven must’ve

574
