577
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:21,060
How did Your Highness know?

578
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:26,380
Heaven shows his mercy.

579
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:28,860
He happened to see

580
00:28:29,300 --> 00:28:30,460
the princess praying for His Majesty

581
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:32,620
in the backyard.

582
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:34,820
Otherwise

583
00:28:34,820 --> 00:28:36,220
her love to her father

584
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:38,980
