597
00:29:05,340 --> 00:29:07,700
Besides, the princess is noble,

598
00:29:07,940 --> 00:29:09,060
innocent,

599
00:29:09,540 --> 00:29:10,580
and filial.

600
00:29:10,860 --> 00:29:12,780
She’s loved by His Majesty and Her Highness,

601
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:14,180
