615
00:29:59,780 --> 00:30:00,820
Do what?

616
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:07,420
Huirou, say something.

617
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:10,620
Now Lady Zhang wrongs you,

618
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:12,980
