622
00:30:22,620 --> 00:30:23,940
Huirou, what’s wrong with you?

623
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:28,740
You went to the lakeside to pray for your father,

624
00:30:29,060 --> 00:30:30,660
if it were not Huaiji,

625
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:32,140
