626
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,820
Now you don’t even want to

627
00:30:34,820 --> 00:30:35,860
explain for yourself?

628
00:30:36,340 --> 00:30:37,260
Madam Miao,

629
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:40,140
Huirou is so young

630
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:43,140
and got wronged,

631
00:30:43,820 --> 00:30:44,820
and questioned today.

632
00:30:45,540 --> 00:30:46,660
She must’ve been scared.

633
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:49,340
How can she figure it out now.

634
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:51,580
Take your time.

635
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:02,460
Don’t worry.

636
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:04,140
You are lucky.

637
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:05,980
Just now the princess is born,

638
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:07,540
