644
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:36,700
Feel uncomfortable?

645
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,260
Where’s Huirou?

646
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:44,060
I hear Huirou is calling me.

647
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:53,940
In the past, Zhao Feiyan

648
00:31:54,380 --> 00:31:56,020
accused Madam Ban of cursing.

649
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:58,260
Emperor Cheng of Han interrogated Madam Ban.

650
00:31:58,580 --> 00:31:59,620
She answered

651
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:01,780
“I know that the life span is destined,

652
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:03,260
and that the rich and the poor
are doomed by the heaven.

653
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:05,700
Being virtuous has not yet been blessed,

654
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:07,740
