659
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:15,220
That’s why I won’t do it.”

660
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,740
This kid is right.

661
00:32:19,940 --> 00:32:21,060
Huirou is young,

662
00:32:22,260 --> 00:32:23,660
