663
00:32:24,620 --> 00:32:26,060
She can’t quote the classics

664
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:28,020
and can’t explain it right now.

665
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:30,660
Or maybe she doesn’t want to

666
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:33,540
explain in front of so many people.

667
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:35,820
But what she said

668
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:37,580
is the same meaning

669
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,100
of what Madam Ban’s

670
00:32:41,740 --> 00:32:43,020
said.

671
00:32:47,660 --> 00:32:48,900
Are you comparing me to

672
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:50,060
Zhao Feiyan who wrecked the country?

673
00:32:51,740 --> 00:32:52,460
No.

674
00:32:54,020 --> 00:32:54,780
Your Highness.

675
00:32:59,940 --> 00:33:01,060
His Majesty is awake.

676
00:33:02,140 --> 00:33:04,140
He wants to see Princess Fukang.

677
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:15,140
Go, let’s go to see your father.

678
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:34,980
I just saw

679
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,620
Huirou vaguely

680
