697
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:23,020
Ask him to check on His Majesty again.

698
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,220
Yes.

699
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:32,620
Huirou is my most important treasure.

700
00:34:34,700 --> 00:34:36,300
You don’t want your mother to know

701
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:38,380
even if you were criticized by her

702
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:40,540
