703
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:43,180
Let me guess,

704
00:34:45,180 --> 00:34:47,820
it must be because I was too sick

705
00:34:49,380 --> 00:34:52,940
that the Empress didn’t tell your mother

706
00:34:52,940 --> 00:34:54,180
for fear that it might hurt her baby,

707
00:34:54,860 --> 00:34:56,420
