710
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:06,140
But you didn’t want your mother to know

711
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:07,860
that I was so sick.

712
00:35:08,940 --> 00:35:09,980
Am I right?

713
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:14,620
Huirou,

714
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:18,020
I wronged you.

715
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,540
There, there.

716
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:30,460
Why does she

717
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,300
have your personalities?

718
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:37,940
There, there.

719
00:35:37,940 --> 00:35:38,940
Don’t cry.

720
00:36:03,860 --> 00:36:07,460
= Di Qing, courtesy name Hanchen =

721
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:08,180
Sir.

722
00:36:10,060 --> 00:36:11,380
You asked me to come

723
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:12,460
