725
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,180
Take a seat.

726
00:36:19,140 --> 00:36:22,300
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =

727
00:36:23,740 --> 00:36:25,060
I want you to eat some porridge.

728
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,300
Porridge?

729
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:40,740
The porridge is made with

730
00:36:41,940 --> 00:36:43,220
Champa Rice from the first harvest

731
00:36:43,220 --> 00:36:45,220
grown here.

732
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:47,820
The harvest is 30 percent

733
00:36:47,900 --> 00:36:49,060
