736
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:54,660
to thank us for giving them

737
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:57,460
the new seed of grain a year ago.

738
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:01,780
Tastes good.

739
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:04,620
I’ll go to Yaozhou soon.

740
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,300
Yaozhou?

741
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:13,180
You are demoted?

742
00:37:15,060 --> 00:37:15,820
Why?

743
00:37:17,020 --> 00:37:19,420
You made extraordinary contributions to Yan’an.

744
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:21,660
You’ve resumed forts nearby,

745
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:23,540
repelled the enemy,

746
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:25,100
reassured the people, built farming land

747
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:25,860
