748
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:27,820
Who here does not respect you?

749
00:37:28,660 --> 00:37:30,340
Why on earth can you be demoted?

750
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:32,460
Sit down.

751
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:41,500
I’m just doing my job somewhere else,

752
00:37:41,940 --> 00:37:43,500
