753
00:37:44,380 --> 00:37:45,860
There must be a reason.

754
00:37:46,380 --> 00:37:47,540
The losing war

755
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,180
has nothing to do with you.

756
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:51,740
You firmly stood against the attack.

757
00:37:51,940 --> 00:37:52,820
The truth shows

758
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:54,260
what you said is completely right.

759
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,100
It is my mistake.

760
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:04,980
If His Majesty is not a kind emperor,

761
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:06,460
what I did

762
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:09,460
