774
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:48,900
Sympathetic or weary of war?

775
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:51,860
That’s hard to tell.

776
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:56,380
I, Fan Zhongyan

777
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:59,540
