780
00:39:08,020 --> 00:39:09,380
Before I took the position,

781
00:39:10,140 --> 00:39:13,140
I did want to win a huge war,

782
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:15,460
kill the enemies, take down places,

783
00:39:15,780 --> 00:39:17,260
and show our power,

784
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:19,300
so that I can settle down the west with my credits.

785
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:21,860
But after I came here,

786
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:24,620
after I saw the soldiers

787
00:39:24,740 --> 00:39:25,700
and people

788
