In the letter I wrote to Yuanhao,

793
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:49,460
I said both armies are serving their leaders.

794
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:50,740
They are all loyal people.

795
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,780
I don’t want to see loyal people

796
00:39:52,780 --> 00:39:53,900
killing each other

797
00:39:53,900 --> 00:39:54,900
having blood flood.

798
00:39:56,780 --> 00:39:58,700
I mean what I said.

799
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:01,300
If you say this is the fear of wars,

800
00:40:02,220 --> 00:40:04,260
and it affects subordinates’ morale,

801
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:08,660
it might be.

802
00:40:10,180 --> 00:40:11,500
I have nothing to explain for myself

803
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:14,180
