806
00:40:21,580 --> 00:40:22,500
Tell him

807
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:23,820
I’m on my way.

808
00:40:24,460 --> 00:40:25,180
Yes.

809
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:42,660
General Di.

810
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:50,620
Are you…

811
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:56,300
It is your duty now

812
00:40:56,820 --> 00:40:58,300
to protect our land and people.

813
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:01,300
To cease the war,

814
00:41:01,940 --> 00:41:04,820
does it really

815
00:41:05,460 --> 00:41:07,460
cost blood

816
00:41:07,460 --> 00:41:08,580
