817
00:41:10,020 --> 00:41:13,100
That’s a question for you to answer.

818
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:38,620
Joining the army is not the only way
to serve the state.

819
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,980
People should make the best of themselves.

820
00:41:41,340 --> 00:41:44,620
= Zhang Zai, courtesy name Zihou =

821
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:47,300
Zihou,

822
00:41:48,260 --> 00:41:50,540
your father named you Zhang Zai

823
00:41:50,540 --> 00:41:51,500
with courtesy name Zihou,

824
00:41:52,620 --> 00:41:54,220
I think because he hopes

825
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:57,660
you can undertake great tasks with high morality.

826
00:41:58,540 --> 00:41:59,900
Your writings

827
00:42:00,140 --> 00:42:01,780
also show gentleness

828
00:42:01,980 --> 00:42:03,820
and broadness.

829
00:42:08,220 --> 00:42:10,420
Confucian scholars have their own famous belief,

830
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:12,900
why do you have to serve the military?

831
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:18,540
I give you the book the Doctrine of Mean,

832
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:23,340
hoping in the future

833
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,780
the court can have a great scholar

834
00:42:25,780 --> 00:42:27,620
who has thorough study on the Confucius

835
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:32,740
and who can carry it forward.

836
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:35,580
Yes, sir.

